lyrics:
[Verse]
In this world, so twisted and confused
I'm just a stranger in a body abused
Rejected and alienated, I'm feeling so alone
A foreign organ in a place I can't call home

[Chorus]
But I won't crumble, won't be torn apart
I'll rise above the chaos, create my own art
Embrace the darkness, find my own light
Defy the rejection, take flight into the night
